Since May 9, the heaviest rainfall this year has swept most of southern China. The precipitation lasts long with a large amount of rainfall. The heavy rainfall covers provincial regions including Guangdong, Guangxi and Sichuan. Check the video to find out more. (Video courtesy of Weather China, online weather service of the China Meteorological Administration) (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)